  "detailed_description": "BIT.TRIP RUNNER is more than just a game; it's a retro-inspired masterpiece with pixel art that pays homage to classic gaming while delivering a modern and immersive adventure. The simplicity of the controls makes it accessible to all, but mastering the game demands skill, timing, and a deep connection to the music. This unique blend of challenging gameplay and captivating aesthetics sets BIT.TRIP RUNNER apart, making it a must-play for both genre enthusiasts and newcomers. <br><br>Notably, in the 2011 Independent Games Festival, it earned the esteemed Excellence in Visual Art award and received honorable mentions for the Seumas McNally Grand Prize and the Excellence in Audio awards, solidifying its status as an outstanding gaming experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63710/extras/3ad90f018e4467e8173d989fe441c27d.poster.avif?t=1700025629\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63710/extras/3ad90f018e4467e8173d989fe441c27d.webm?t=1700025629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63710/extras/3ad90f018e4467e8173d989fe441c27d.mp4?t=1700025629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
